- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper discusses the concept of essential systems and their supports, which are related to control theory. 
- cs.DS (Dynamical Systems) is another possible category as the paper deals with differential equations and their resultant. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the degree and order bounds for the sparse differential resultant, which are related to geometric properties of the system. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is the least likely category, but still possible as the paper may have applications in computer graphics and geometric modeling.
